    <section class="content-section">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Key Benefits of PAMM Accounts</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            PAMM accounts bridge the gap between skilled traders and investors, creating a symbiotic relationship built
            on performance and transparency. Discover the advantages that make this system a powerful tool for your
            capital.
        </p>

        <div class="benefits-grid">
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 001.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 01-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 01-4.5 0m3.75 2.311a7.5 7.5 0 00-7.5 0" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Access to Professional Expertise</h3>
                <p>Much like a cooperative pools resources, a PAMM account allows you to leverage the skills of seasoned
                    traders. You don't need to be a trading expert; you simply entrust your capital to one.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-item">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0011.667 0l3.181-3.183m-4.991-2.69l-3.182-3.182a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0l-3.182 3.182" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">True Alignment of Interests</h3>
                <p>There are no promises of fixed gains. A serious manager's goal is to grow the fund, as their own
                    capital is invested alongside yours and their main profit comes from performance fees. They win only
                    when you win.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-item">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Flexibility and Liquidity</h3>
                <p>Depending on the broker and manager, trading periods can be as short as two weeks instead of a full
                    month. This means you could potentially access part of your profits more frequently, offering
                    greater liquidity.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-item">
                <div class="benefit-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.286zm0 13.036h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Transparency and Security</h3>
                <p>You maintain full control of your account. You can monitor performance in real-time, set your own
                    risk limits, and deposit or withdraw funds according to the agreement. The manager can trade, but
                    cannot access your funds directly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

